\\\" for advertisers, with data showing 300% growth in searches for brands during the opening ceremony compared to Tokyo.\", \"from\": 4111, \"to\": 4345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4198, \"end\": 4203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2731776652307925e-25, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4339, \"end\": 4344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0814099207179382e-19, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dory Ellis Garfinkle\", \"from\": 4111, \"to\": 4131}, {\"ngram\": \"chief marketing officer\", \"from\": 4133, \"to\": 4156}, {\"ngram\": \"brand strategy firm Siegel+Gale\", \"from\": 4160, \"to\": 4191}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"comeback Olympics\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4227}, {\"ngram\": \"advertisers\", \"from\": 4233, \"to\": 4244}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4255}, {\"ngram\": \"300% growth\", \"from\": 4264, \"to\": 4275}, {\"ngram\": \"searches\", \"from\": 4279, \"to\": 4287}, {\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 4292, \"to\": 4298}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris' success is a major relief for the IOC, which had been struggling to attract younger audiences needed to justify multi-billion-dollar TV and sponsorship deals.\", \"from\": 4347, \"to\": 4512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4347, \"end\": 4352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2731776652307925e-25, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4388, \"end\": 4391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6844134197387482e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a major relief\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4379}, {\"ngram\": \"younger audiences\", \"from\": 4430, \"to\": 4447}, {\"ngram\": \"multi-billion-dollar TV and sponsorship deals\", \"from\": 4466, \"to\": 4511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It successfully navigated a potentially risky move to deepen product placement, with no major backlash overSamsung phoneson medal podiums or Louis Vuitton suitcases during the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 4514, \"to\": 4707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4655, \"end\": 4668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9515704422056059e-28, \"text\": \"Louis Vuitton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_Vuitton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a potentially risky move\", \"from\": 4540, \"to\": 4564}, {\"ngram\": \"product placement\", \"from\": 4575, \"to\": 4592}, {\"ngram\": \"no major backlash overSamsung phoneson medal podiums\", \"from\": 4599, \"to\": 4651}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Expect more in future Games, IOC officials say.\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4737, \"end\": 4740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6844134197387482e-34, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r